article.description: Lewis Sullivan had 17 points and seven rebounds as UAB topped Middle Tennessee 70-61 in the first round of the Conference USA Tourney on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Sullivan scores 17 to lead UAB over Middle Tennessee 70-61
article.linkText: Sullivan scores 17 to lead UAB over Middle Tennessee 70-61
article.story: FRISCO, Texas -- Lewis Sullivan had 17 points and seven rebounds as UAB topped Middle Tennessee 70-61 in the first round of the Conference USA Tourney on Wednesday night. Zack Bryant had 15 points for UAB (19-13). Jalen Perry added 14 points. Jeremiah Bell had 12 points for UAB. Donovan Sims had 22 points for the Blue Raiders (11-21). Karl Gamble added 18 points and 13 rebounds.
